\ip Jon in aposol riti s…ô Iesu rokeikei p…®k. In r…®rai n…ôkuku…ô me i Jon, Fas Jon, Seken Jon, m…®ne Namba Tri Jon. In r…®rai n…ôkuku…ô me n…ôha ipaka t…® nuk 90. Fas Jon r…ôv…ôha…° m nakalasia me m…®ni m…ô ir…ôha tuham…ôkeikei mh…ôsiari t…® nahat…ôn eiku…ô me kamo nahat…ôn eiku…ô me h…ôkoui irapw ir…ôha ia suatuk atukwatukw. Nahat…ôn eiku…ô me n…ôha kamh…ôni m…ô Iesu r…®pko mh…ô in Kristo, T…®ni Kumwes…ôn. H…ôni m…ô Kumwes…ôn r…®pkuvehe mh…ô mo in i…ôrmama r…ômwhen ia k…®taha. Jon rokeikei m…ô nakalasia me tuh…ôukur…ôn m…ô Iesu in Kumwes…ôn m…®ne in mwi i…ôrmama. Jon rokeikei m…ô truvehi ut…ô n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien s…ôv…ôi nakalasia me pw…ôh h…ôrer …ôknek…®n ia nahat…ôt…ôien s…ôv…ônraha ia Iesu Kristo mamho nokeikeiien. In r…®ni m…ô k…®taha tsam…ôkeikei mhokeikei k…®taha me, mamh…ôsiai n…ô…°kiariien me s…ôv…ôi Kumwes…ôn. Tr…®ni m…®nu…ô samo iam…®nha ir…ô, s…ôukur…ôn m…ô k…®taha n…®pwn…ôti Kumwes…ôn me.  
\c 1  
\s1 N…ô…°kiariien s…ôv…ôi N…®m…®ruien  
\p
\v 1 \x - \xo 1:1 \xt Jon 1:1-2,4, 1Jon 2:13-14\x*N…ô…°kiariien i s…ôk…®maha ram…ôvisau N…ô…°kiariien s…ô r…®nar…ô raka fwe tui n…ôp…®n t…®pr…ôn…ô ramiw…ôn ihi. K…®maha iah…ôuv…ôre…°i raka N…ô…°kiariien n…ôha, mh…ôtoni ia n…ônimemaha, mh…ôspau ir…ô, mh…ôrapi ia r…ô…°…®maha. N…ô…°kiariien n…ôha in N…®m…®ruien.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 1:2 \xt Jon 1:14\x*N…®m…®ruien i r…®m…ôier pehe tukumaha. K…®maha iah…ôn…ôtoni mh…ôukur…ôn m…ô in n…®p…ôrhienien. N…ôn…ô t…ôkwt…ôkwuni iaham…ôni irapw N…®m…®ruien Rer…®n i tukumiaha. Fwe kupw…ôn in r…®namar…ô irau Tata Kumwes…ôn, n…ôn…ô mar…ô mier pehe tukumaha.  
\v 3 Iaham…ôni irapw tukumiaha narimnari me i iah…ôn…ôtoni mh…ôre…°i m…ô k…®miaha tih…ôuvehe mho p…ôri nari k…®taha m k…®miaha. P…ôrhien k…®maha iahamo p…ôri nari k…®maha Tata Kumwes…ôn m…®ne T…®ni, Iesu Kristo.  
\v 4 \x - \xo 1:4 \xt Jon 16:24\x*N…ô…°kiariien me i iahamrai rauvehe tukumiaha m…ô tro rer…®maha ra…°ien.   
\s1 Nav…ônien ia nukuraanien  
