\v 23 \x - \xo 2:23 \xt Jon 5:23, 15:23, 1Jon 4:15, 5:1, 2Jon 9\x*I…ôrmama s…ô rani neiku…ôien ia T…®ni Kumwes…ôn, Tata Kumwes…ôn r…®pkar…ô mh…ô tukwe. M…ôt…ô i…ôrmama s…ô rani irapw T…®ni Kumwes…ôn, Tata Kumwes…ôn in mwi ramar…ô tukwe.   
\p
\v 24 N…ô…°kiariien n…ôha k…®miaha hi…ôm…ôre…°i k…®nani fwe nukunen tih…ôtui amasan tukwe pw…ôh r…ôpwit …ôknek…®n ia rer…®miaha ia n…ôp…®n me. Tr…®ni m…®nu…ô n…ô…°kiariien n…ôha hi…ôm…ôre…°i k…®nani fwe nukunen r…ôpwit …ôknek…®n ia rer…®miaha n…ôp…®n me, k…®miaha mwi tih…ôpwit …ôknek…®n ia T…®ni Kumwes…ôn m…®ne Tata s…ôv…ônhi.  
