\v 27 \x - \xo 2:27 \xt Jon 16:13\x*K…®miaha hi…ôuv…ôuvehi raka N…ôn…®mw…®n s…ô Kristo r…®n…ôt…ô…°i pen ia k…®miaha. N…ôn…®mw…®n n…ôha r…®nar…ô raka ia k…®miaha ro pen hi…ôpk…ôtui mh…ô mwi i…ôrmama riti m…ô trahat…ôn k…®miaha. M…ôt…ô n…ôn…®mw…®n s…ô Kristo r…®n…ôt…ô…°i pen ia k…®miaha ramahat…ôn k…®miaha ia narimnari me pam. N…ôn…ô narimnari me n…ôha ramahat…ôn k…®miaha ir…ô ro n…®p…ôrhienien r…®pko mh…ô neiku…ôien. Ro iam…®nhi ir…ô tih…ôpwit …ôknek…®n ia Kristo r…ômwhen ia N…ôn…®mw…®n n…ôha r…®nahat…ôn k…®miaha ir…ô.   
