\v 29 \x - \xo 2:29 \xt 1Jon 3:7,10\x*K…®miaha hi…ôuv…ôukur…ôn raka m…ô noien s…ôv…ôi Kumwes…ôn ratukwatukw. Ro iam…®nhi ir…ô hi…ôuv…ôukur…ôn mwi m…ô n…ôrmama s…ôm…ôme kamho noien atukwatukw ir…ôha n…®pwn…ôt…®n me.   
